<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>What if you could only loot from inventory? -OPINIONS</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?TheBlack">TheBlack</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 3:34 p.m. 7/6/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> What if you could only loot from inventory? -OPINIONS<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2144" TARGET=_self>Going out on a limb on looting</A> (Ice)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>

<BR>What if you were unable to loot any item worn or carried, but you could loot from inventory, including looting items out of containers within one's inventory? Would this be a more "fair" system of looting?
<P>&gt; Im not sure how most people would feel about, this im sure the
<BR>&gt; die hard pks wouldnt like it at all,. Anyway i feel that when
<BR>&gt; you killsome all you can loot off that person is the money they
<BR>&gt; have on them, maybe even one item from a bag, which would be
<BR>&gt; fine,. But no armor, weapons etc...
<P>&gt; My reason being is, what i really hate are when you see these
<BR>&gt; pk's killing people mainly armor warriors, that are half dead, 4
<BR>&gt; levels above them whatever it may be, and then looting, You ask
<BR>&gt; why? Because these guys dont equip anything, at the most they
<BR>&gt; might equip a nice rusty dagger, or something, but they just
<BR>&gt; kill you with there spells and take that banded armor, or piece
<BR>&gt; of plate that you have been working your ass of for,. ITs just
<BR>&gt; sad watching people killing people naked, and then watching the
<BR>&gt; people getting killed be bagging there stuff for that they cant
<BR>&gt; loot there armor and weapons, the reason i said money and
<BR>&gt; something in a bag, in the bag they might have a precious stone
<BR>&gt; they have got off a monster or another item that might be worth
<BR>&gt; money but wouldnt have these warriors bagging there stuff, while
<BR>&gt; being killed, or haveing a full set of bronze plate mail and
<BR>&gt; never leaveing town with it on. Its just to easy for wizards who
<BR>&gt; are like it or not the most powerful class in the game, be able
<BR>&gt; to root, and Blast your ass while they are naked, and knowing
<BR>&gt; they wont loose a thing. And its nothing to do with well a
<BR>&gt; warrior or cleric should be grouped, alot of it is when we are
<BR>&gt; sitting there waiting for hitpoints or something when it
<BR>&gt; happens. I dont mind being killed, and i love pvp combat. All im
<BR>&gt; saying is its kinda not fair haveing one person walking around
<BR>&gt; but naked without a thing to loose, while the other is a Walking
<BR>&gt; Fort Knox.. :)
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
